name: Hand in Hand | Cut Paper
description:
"How about you and me hold hands?
And we’ll walk together.
And we’ll take each day one step at a time.
We’ll try not to worry about tomorrow.
Because tomorrow’s too far away.
But we’ll enjoy the moment we’re in.
Because right now i don’t want to be anywhere else but walking with you.
Your hand in mine is a beautiful thing."

Inspired by the words written by my friend, and jewelry designer, Lisa Leonard, to her son David, this sentiment is a wish we can all relate to in any close relationship as we journey together. 

-----

Created from a single sheet of paper, each laser cutting is a replica of the design Lori meticulously cut by hand. Each piece is cut with a high-powered laser, which creates an exquisite piece of art with the delicacy of fine lace. 
 
Available Paper Colors: Off-White, Black 
Approximate Artwork Size: 16” x 20”
Cut upon order, allow approximately 2 weeks.
Signed by Lori Danelle

Carefully packaged and shipped in a rigid mailer to protect your artwork. Only ground shipping is available for this item.

*** Also available as a wrapped canvas or print  ***

name: Double Fingerprint {Text} Cut Paper
description:
Turn your fingerprint into a custom piece of art. Perfect for celebrating a wedding or anniversary!

Paper Cut Artist Lori Danelle creates stunning works of art with a personal touch. Using a sheet of 11" x 14" acid-free paper and a craft knife, she captures the essence of a couple's unique relationship by carefully hand-cutting each sheet with the unique pattern that make up each partner's fingerprints. By cutting each piece by hand, that artist is able to magnify and replicate their one-of-a-kind prints in striking detail, giving them the delicacy and intricacy of fine lace.

A beautiful way to capture a couple's romantic bond, this custom-made artwork is finished with both partner's names and a heart cut into the space between their prints (equation) or the names and a special date below the prints (simple). Using her meticulous art making method, Lori crafts each print in a personalized double-portrait that serves as a reminder to embrace the little things that make the people we're close to uniquely wonderful. Handmade in Nashville.

***Laser Cut Option also available:

Each 11" x 14" Laser Cut Double Fingerprint piece starts the very same way our Hand Cut versions do: hours spent meticulously going over each print in order to prepare them for layout and cutting. This attention to detail at the very beginning allows the artist to magnify and replicate their one-of-a-kind prints in striking detail, giving them the delicacy and intricacy of fine lace.

The difference comes in how the artwork is cut. Using precision lasers, the sheet of paper is still cut with the unique pattern that make up each partner's fingerprints, but it is done so at a more economical price to you. Because a high-power laser is used to literally burn away the paper — leaving behind a smooth, finished edge — a minimal amount of discoloration can be possible.

You will receive a stamp kit with detailed instructions in order to complete the imprints of your fingers and a place to select the names or initials to be included.

In the same package, you will receive an addressed mailer with postage paid so your completed prints can be sent to the artist.

Shipped in a rigid mailer to protect your artwork. Only ground shipping is available for the item. At this time, this item can only be shipped to the contiguous 48 states.

See FAQs & Policies for additional information.

name: You Are My Sunshine | Cut Paper
description:
I, like many, grew up with my Mom singing You Are My Sunshine to me & always felt that in some special way, it was FOR me. So, when I had children of my own, the song quickly became part of my repertoire.

I created this piece for my girls. I hope they know the joy they have brought into my life. 

Some days, they practically are up there on that ladder pushing the grey clouds apart that have settled on my heart after a tiring or bad day. And the wonderful thing is, they don’t have to do anything to make me feel instantaneously lighter. They bring me joy because they are them. 

Well, that & cute little hedgehogs. Because really, how can hedgehogs not make you smile?

My hope is that this piece will make you smile too. 

Created from a single sheet of paper, each laser cutting is a replica of the design Lori meticulously cut by hand. Each piece is cut with a high-powered laser, which creates an exquisite piece of art with the delicacy of fine lace.

Signed by Lori Danelle
